config BH_ARC_TELEMETRY
	bool "Tenstorrent BH-arc live telemetry sensor"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_TENSTORRENT_BH_ARC_TELEMETRY_ENABLED
	depends on SMBUS
	help
	  Enable Zephyr sensor driver that reads live telemetry from a
	  tenstorrent,bh-arc (SMC) device node via SMBus.  Each sample issues a
	  byte-data write to CMFW_SMBUS_TELEMETRY_READ_CRC followed by a block
	  read from CMFW_SMBUS_TELEMETRY_READ_CRC_DATA.  Reads are served
	  through the RTIO submit API.  Channel-to-telemetry-tag mappings are defined in the
	  device tree.
